snippet.title: A Field of Flowers and Stars - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A Field of Flowers and Stars launches on August 6th, 2020

You can find the game on itch.io:
https://watercress.itch.io/

Directed by TheAlchemyst (@alchworks)
Edited by TheAlchemyst
BGM by Paul Robins
Raine voiced by Natalie Van Sistine(@nvansistine)
Juneau voiced by Lily Lammers(@homulily)

A collaboration between Watercress, Somnova Studios, and Sarchalen Visual Media
